== OLLMchat API - Package Overview ==

This documentation covers the OLLMchat application and its libraries.

== Application ==

* libollmapp — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMapp.html|OLLMapp]]''. Main application: window, settings dialogs. Entry point and window management.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMapp.SettingsDialog.html|SettingsDialog]]'' — ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMapp.SettingsDialog.MainDialog.html|MainDialog]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMapp.SettingsDialog.ConnectionsPage.html|ConnectionsPage]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMapp.SettingsDialog.ModelsPage.html|ModelsPage]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMapp.SettingsDialog.ProjectsPage.html|ProjectsPage]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMapp.SettingsDialog.ToolsPage.html|ToolsPage]]''. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMapp.SettingsDialog.Rows.html|Rows]]'' — row widgets for settings.

== Core libraries ==

* libollmchat — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.html|OLLMchat]]''. LLM chat client: Ollama/OpenAI-compatible API, tool calling, streaming, history, and configuration without GTK.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Client.html|Client]]'' — API communication and chat entry point. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Message.html|Message]]'' — chat message representation.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.html|Call]]'' — API call implementations. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.Base.html|Base]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.Chat.html|Chat]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.Embed.html|Embed]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.Models.html|Models]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.Create.html|Create]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.Delete.html|Delete]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.Pull.html|Pull]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Call.Version.html|Version]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Response.html|Response]]'' — Response types for API results. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Response.Base.html|Base]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Response.Chat.html|Chat]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Response.CallFunction.html|CallFunction]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Response.ToolCall.html|ToolCall]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Tool.html|Tool]]'' — Function calling (tools, params, requests). ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Tool.BaseTool.html|BaseTool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Tool.Function.html|Function]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Tool.Param.html|Param]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Tool.RequestBase.html|RequestBase]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.History.html|History]]'' — Session persistence and list. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.History.Manager.html|Manager]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.History.Session.html|Session]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.History.SessionBase.html|SessionBase]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Settings.html|Settings]]'' — Configuration (connections, models, usage). ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Settings.Connection.html|Connection]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Settings.Config2.html|Config2]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Settings.ConnectionModels.html|ConnectionModels]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Settings.ModelUsage.html|ModelUsage]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Agent.html|Agent]]'' — Agent interface and implementations. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Agent.Interface.html|Interface]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Agent.Base.html|Base]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Agent.Factory.html|Factory]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Agent.JustAsk.html|JustAsk]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Agent.JustAskFactory.html|JustAskFactory]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Prompt.html|Prompt]]'' — Prompt templates for agents. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Prompt.Template.html|Template]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.ChatPermission.html|ChatPermission]]'' — Permission provider for tool access. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.ChatPermission.Provider.html|Provider]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.ChatPermission.Dummy.html|Dummy]]''.

* liboctools — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.html|OLLMtools]]''. Built-in tools; registered via ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchat.Tool.html|Tool]]'' and used by the chat/agent stack.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.ReadFile.html|ReadFile]]'' — Read file contents. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.ReadFile.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.ReadFile.Request.html|Request]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.WriteFile.html|WriteFile]]'' — Write file contents. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.WriteFile.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.WriteFile.Request.html|Request]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.RunCommand.html|RunCommand]]'' — Run shell commands. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.RunCommand.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.RunCommand.Request.html|Request]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.WebFetch.html|WebFetch]]'' — Fetch URLs. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.WebFetch.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.WebFetch.Request.html|Request]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.GoogleSearch.html|GoogleSearch]]'' — Web search. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.GoogleSearch.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.GoogleSearch.Config.html|Config]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.CodebaseSearch.html|CodebaseSearch]]'' — Semantic codebase search. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.CodebaseSearch.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.CodebaseSearch.Request.html|Request]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.HuggingFace.html|HuggingFace]]'' — Hugging Face model search and download. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.HuggingFace.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.HuggingFace.Request.html|Request]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.Child.html|Child]]'' — Child/sub-agent tool. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.Child.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.Child.Agent.html|Agent]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.Child.Factory.html|Factory]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.EditMode.html|EditMode]]'' — Edit-in-place streaming. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.EditMode.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.EditMode.Stream.html|Stream]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMtools.Registry.html|Registry]]'' — Tool registration.

* libocfiles — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.html|OLLMfiles]]''. File and project management: buffers, files, folders, project list, tree-sitter AST paths, diff/patch.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.File.html|File]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.Folder.html|Folder]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.FileBase.html|FileBase]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.FileBuffer.html|FileBuffer]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.ProjectManager.html|ProjectManager]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.ProjectFiles.html|ProjectFiles]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.Tree.html|Tree]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.TreeBase.html|TreeBase]]''. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.Diff.Patch.html|Patch]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.Diff.Differ.html|Differ]]''.

* libollmchatgtk — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.html|OLLMchatGtk]]''. Chat widget, history browser, tool permission UI, model usage list. Application-facing GTK pieces.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.ChatWidget.html|ChatWidget]]'' — main chat container. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.ChatView.html|ChatView]]'' — message display. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.ChatInput.html|ChatInput]]'' — input area. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.ChatBar.html|ChatBar]]'' — top bar. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.HistoryBrowser.html|HistoryBrowser]]'' — session list. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.ChatPermission.html|ChatPermission]]'' — permission UI.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.List.html|List]]'' — Model usage list/filter/sort. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.List.ModelUsageFilter.html|ModelUsageFilter]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.List.ModelUsageSort.html|ModelUsageSort]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.List.ModelUsageFactory.html|ModelUsageFactory]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.List.SortedList.html|SortedList]]''. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.Tools.html|Tools]]'' — Tool permission UI. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMchatGtk.Tools.Permission.html|Permission]]''.

== RPC and daemons ==

* libocrpc — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMrpc.html|OLLMrpc]]''. Binary RPC client and wire types for ollmfilesd (Unix socket / stdio / TCP) and HTTPS JSON APIs. Overview and usage examples on the namespace page.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMrpc.Client.html|Client]]'' — connect and call. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMrpc.Request.html|Request]]'' / ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMrpc.Response.html|Response]]'' — envelopes. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMrpc.CallParam.html|CallParam]]'' — typed params. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMrpc.Bin.html|Bin]]'' — Serializable, Stream, Json. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMrpc.Transport.html|Transport]]'' — daemon listen/connection.

* ollmfilesd — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfilesd.html|OLLMfilesd]]''. Headless file and semantic-index daemon (RPC over stdio or TCP).

== Semantic search ==

* libocfiles (vector metadata) — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.SQT.html|OLLMfiles.SQT]]''. SQLite vector metadata used by the file daemon and codebase search.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMfiles.SQT.VectorMetadata.html|VectorMetadata]]'' — per-chunk embedding metadata rows.

== Hugging Face and Ollama web ==

* libochf — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMhf.html|OLLMhf]]''. Hugging Face Hub model catalog (search, detail, GGUF download).

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMhf.Model.html|Model]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMhf.ModelArray.html|ModelArray]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMhf.Download.html|Download]]''. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMhf.Param.html|Param]]'' — search query params.

* libollamaweb — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OllamaWeb.html|OllamaWeb]]''. Live search and model metadata from ollama.com.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OllamaWeb.Search.html|Search]]'' — ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OllamaWeb.Search.Client.html|Client]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OllamaWeb.Search.Service.html|Service]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OllamaWeb.Model.html|Model]]''.

== MCP and sandboxing ==

* libocmcp — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMmcp.html|OLLMmcp]]''. MCP (Model Context Protocol) client: load servers, discover tools, expose as agent tools.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMmcp.Loader.html|Loader]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMmcp.Registry.html|Registry]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMmcp.Tool.html|Tool]]''. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMmcp.Client.html|Client]]'' — stdio and HTTP transports.

* libocbwrap — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMbwrap.html|OLLMbwrap]]''. Bubblewrap overlay and seccomp sandboxing for tool execution.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMbwrap.Bubble.html|Bubble]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMbwrap.Overlay.html|Overlay]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMbwrap.RunSeccomp.html|RunSeccomp]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMbwrap.Scan.html|Scan]]''.

== Markdown parsing and rendering ==

* libocmarkdown — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.html|Markdown]]''. Markdown parsing and document model. Used by skills and chat rendering.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.Parser.html|Parser]]'' — Parse markdown. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.RenderBase.html|RenderBase]]'' — Base renderer.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.Document.html|Document]]'' — Document tree (nodes, blocks, format). ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.Document.Document.html|Document]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.Document.Block.html|Block]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.Document.Node.html|Node]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.Document.Format.html|Format]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.Document.List.html|List]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/Markdown.Document.Render.html|Render]]''.

* libocmarkdowngtk — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/MarkdownGtk.html|MarkdownGtk]]''. GTK markdown rendering for the chat UI.

== Coding and Skills ==

* liboccoder — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.html|OLLMcoder]]''. Code-editor and task/skill layer: skills, tasks, GTK source view. Skill-based task creation, refinement, and execution.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Skill.html|Skill]]'' — Skill definitions, runner, manager, templates. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Skill.Runner.html|Runner]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Skill.Manager.html|Manager]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Skill.Factory.html|Factory]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Skill.Definition.html|Definition]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Skill.PromptTemplate.html|PromptTemplate]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Task.html|Task]]'' — Task list, details, tool runs, steps, result parsing. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Task.List.html|List]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Task.Details.html|Details]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Task.Tool.html|Tool]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Task.Step.html|Step]]'', ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Task.ResultParser.html|ResultParser]]''.
  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.Agent.html|Agent]]'' — Coding agent. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.AgentFactory.html|AgentFactory]]'' — Factory. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/OLLMcoder.SourceView.html|SourceView]]'' — Code editor widget.

== Database ==

* libocsqlite — namespace: ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/SQ.html|SQ]]''. SQLite wrapper. Used by libocfiles and vector metadata.

  * ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/SQ.Database.html|Database]]'' — DB connection. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/SQ.Query.html|Query]]'' — Prepared statements. ''[[https://roojs.github.io/OLLMchat/ollmchat/SQ.Schema.html|Schema]]'' — Schema definition.

== Reference ==

  * [[https://vala.dev|Vala]] — Vala language site (external).
